  "detailed_description": "\"In life and death, in the paradise between those, you will know your own crime\"<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA visual novel ADV where raw and dead intersect \"Garden of the Vanilla Judgment\"<br />\r\nCircle CHARON's latest work challenging straight from the theme of \"life and death\".<br />\r\nHeroine full voice, delivered in a large volume of 50 CGs (difference included 150 sheets or more).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhere are they going when they remember the sins committed in the past? Everything is told in the story.<br />\r\nThe player will check with his / her eyes. The destiny of their fate.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n※ This work includes grotesque, violence, partly sexual, shocking content.<br />\r\nWe prohibit the purchase of those under 15 years old hard.",
  "about_the_game": "\"In life and death, in the paradise between those, you will know your own crime\"<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA visual novel ADV where raw and dead intersect \"Garden of the Vanilla Judgment\"<br />\r\nCircle CHARON's latest work challenging straight from the theme of \"life and death\".<br />\r\nHeroine full voice, delivered in a large volume of 50 CGs (difference included 150 sheets or more).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhere are they going when they remember the sins committed in the past? Everything is told in the story.<br />\r\nThe player will check with his / her eyes. The destiny of their fate.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n※ This work includes grotesque, violence, partly sexual, shocking content.<br />\r\nWe prohibit the purchase of those under 15 years old hard.",
